  <data key="d2">B人員 is an engineer known for involvement in various maintenance tasks. B人員's primary responsibility appears to be handling the maintenance for C客戶, as indicated by multiple sources. This role involves ensuring the smooth operation of systems and addressing any maintenance issues that arise.

