  <data key="d2">B部門is conducting tests on the SH KVstore engine in a personal testing environment due to anomalies.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is the department handling FIsac data extraction and indexer addition.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is a department involved in handling FISAC data and SH KVstore engine testing.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is involved in handling various tasks related to FISAC data, SH KVstore testing, and LDAP settings.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is involved in adding new indexers and other maintenance tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is another department involved in maintenance activities, including FIsac data retrieval and indexer addition.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is the department responsible for checking host certificates and other tasks.</data>
