  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人員, C客戶) refers to a relationship where B人員 is an engineer responsible for various maintenance tasks associated with C客戶. This includes general maintenance duties and specific issues such as the Splunk SH problem. The maintenance activities are part of broader service commitments, including the Splunk駐點服務202510第四周. On a specific instance, B人員 handled these tasks from 13:30 to 17:30 on January 19, 2026. The role involves both routine and issue-specific maintenance, ensuring that C客戶's systems remain operational and well-maintained.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員handled the maintenance for C客戶from 13:30 to 17:30 on 2025/11/4.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員handled the maintenance for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance task for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員handled the maintenance task for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is responsible for handling maintenance tasks for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員handled the maintenance task for C客戶from 2026/01/05 13:30 to 2026/01/05 17:30.</data>
