<edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="Noah Carter">
  <data key="d7">75.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Noah Carter, in relation to the World Athletics Federation, achieved a significant milestone when he set a new 100-meter sprint record. This accomplishment was officially validated by the World Athletics Federation during a championship event. The validation of Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record underscores his exceptional performance and the recognition it received from the governing body of athletics.

The World Athletics Federation plays a crucial role in overseeing and validating such records, ensuring that they meet the highest standards of athletic achievement. In this case, the federation validated Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship, confirming his outstanding performance and contributing to the legacy of the sport. The consistent validation by the World Athletics Federation highlights the significance of Noah Carter's achievement in the realm of athletics.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.</data>
