<edge source="E客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship (C人員, E客戶) involves C人員 being responsible for various maintenance responsibilities related to E客戶. This includes handling maintenance tasks and providing support services. The role of C人員 encompasses maintaining E客戶's systems, ensuring that all necessary work items are addressed, and performing the required maintenance work. This comprehensive approach ensures that E客戶 receives consistent and effective support for their operational needs.

C人員 is specifically tasked with addressing specific work items related to E客戶. This involves performing maintenance tasks as part of scheduled work items. C人員 is assigned to handle these maintenance tasks, which are detailed in the maintenance record. The responsibilities include maintaining E客戶's systems and executing the necessary tasks outlined in the maintenance documentation.

C人員 has performed specific maintenance tasks for E客戶 on December 30, 2025. This indicates that C人員 is actively engaged in handling maintenance tasks related to E客戶, ensuring that all operational needs are met through consistent and effective support.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handled the maintenance task for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handles maintenance tasks for E客戶, including modifying SASE VPN conditions and adding alerts to SOAR.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided maintenance services for E客戶.</data>
