<edge source="C人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (B客戶, C人員) involves C人員 playing a crucial role in the maintenance activities and tasks for B客戶. This relationship is characterized by C人員's consistent involvement in ensuring the upkeep and functionality of B客戶's systems and operations.

C人員 handles various maintenance activities, including specific engineering tasks. For example, on 2025/12/11 from 09:00 to 18:00, C人員 managed a particular maintenance task for B客戶. This highlights the ongoing nature of their responsibilities and the importance of their role in maintaining B客戶's systems.

The descriptions consistently emphasize that C人員 is involved in handling maintenance tasks for B客戶. This includes performing specific maintenance activities and ensuring that B客戶's systems remain operational. The involvement of C人員 in these tasks underscores their essential contribution to the overall functionality and efficiency of B客戶's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is also involved in handling maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is involved in handling maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is involved in the maintenance activities for B客戶.</data>
